# Repo context — repocards

This repository has a pre-computed context folder at `.repocards/`. **Open `.repocards/AGENT_GUIDE.md` at the start of every task in this project** — before running grep/read on the source, and also when the user asks health-check questions like "are you reading repocards?". The guide routes you to pre-computed cards (architecture, entrypoints, api-surface) and contains self-identification instructions. Typical card read is 10–50× fewer tokens than a grep pass.

Generated by [repocards](https://www.npmjs.com/package/repocards). Re-run `npx repocards index` after code changes.
